{"text":"When the value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":". Keep this property set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}]},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Note","type":"aside"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"title":"MLNAnnotationImage","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"by the map view."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation"}}}